{"word":"G5092 - τιμή - timḗ - tee-may' - Honour","slug":"G5092","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">τιμή</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>timḗ"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>tee-may'"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Honour"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x03C4;&#x03B9;&#x03BC;&#x03B7;&#x0301; - time&#x0304;</b> - <i>tee-may'</i><p/>From <a href=\"#/G5099\">G5099</a>; a <i>value</i>, that is, <i>money</i> paid, or (concretely and collectively) <i>valuables</i>; by analogy <i>esteem</i> (especially of the highest degree), or the <i>dignity</i> itself: - honour, precious, price, some."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/G5091\">G5091</a>, <a href=\"#/G5093\">G5093</a>, <a href=\"#/G5094\">G5094</a>"}]}